  var PREPROCESSOR =

    begin: '#', end: '$',
    keywords: {'meta-keyword': 'define definecs|10 undef ifdef ifndef iflight ifdllcall ifmac ifos2win ifunix else endif lineson linesoff srcfile srcline'},

      hljs.C_BLOCK_COMMENT_MODE

          hljs.C_BLOCK_COMMENT_MODE,
